189
00:11:23.358 --> 00:11:25.088
I must do something.

190
00:11:29.728 --> 00:11:30.958
Yoon Jae Young.

191
00:11:31.628 --> 00:11:32.628
From an objective point of view,

192
00:11:32.628 --> 00:11:34.728
